<h2>Edited Movies</h2>
<% settings = [{title: "Movies Ready To Go", urls: all_urls_done}, {urls: all_urls_half_way + all_urls_just_started, title: "Movies we'd like to add (with your support)"}] %>

  <!-- Nav tabs -->
  <ul class="nav nav-pills" role="tablist">
    <% settings.each_with_index{|setting, idx| %>
      <li role="presentation" <%= "class='active'" if idx == 0 %>><a href="#tab_<%= idx %>" aria-controls="home" role="tab" data-toggle="tab"><span style="font-size:larger;"><%= setting[:title] %> (<%= setting[:urls].size %>)</span></a></li>
    <% } %>
  </ul>

  <!-- Tab panes -->
  <div class="tab-content">
    <% settings.each_with_index{|setting, idx| %>
      <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane <%= "active" if idx == 0 %>" id="tab_<%= idx %>"><%= urls = setting[:urls]; title = setting[:title]; render "views/_list_movies.ecr" %></div>
    <% } %>
  </div>

The above are movies/shows/youtubes that we currently have in our system. 
